Title: Identity Crisis
Plot: Grissom's nemesis, serial killer Paul Millander, reappears and claims a third victim in this gripping episode. The latest slaying matches Millander's previous killings in that it recreates his father's murder.  The killer's next target was born Aug. 17, 1956...which just happens to be Grissom's birthday.
GuestStars: Matt O'Toole, Micole Mercurio, Neil Flynn, Cheryl White, Steve Witting, Devon Alan, Steven M. Gagnon, Ryan James, Frank Novak, Rob Roy Fitzgerald, Jason Azikiwe
